of their host stars.

00:16:00.730 --> 00:16:04.040
These kinds of objects are going to
be really, really exciting things

00:16:04.040 --> 00:16:06.510
to study over the next few decades.

00:16:06.510 --> 00:16:10.100
In addition to all of
