00:28:15.190 --> 00:28:17.640
blue dots are other exoplanets,
particularly giants up here.

00:28:17.640 --> 00:28:21.420
And these pink squares are
planets in our own solar system.

00:28:21.420 --> 00:28:25.480
These 4 lines, hydrogen,
water, rock, and iron,

00:28:25.480 --> 00:28:27.100
